<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style>
	body{
        background-color: #edf7fb;
    }
    .error_wrapper{
        position: absolute;
        color:red;
    }
    .column{
        float:left; 
        width: 50%;
    }
    .question{
        margin:20px;
    }
    #logo{
        position: absolute;
        left: 10px;
        top: 10px;
    }
    #title{
        float:left;
    }
    center{
        clear:both;
    }
    #header{
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        height:115px;
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, #e4f5fc 0%, #bfe8f9 50%, #9fd8ef 63%, #2ab0ed 100%); /* FF3.6-15 */
        padding-top: 15px;
</style>
<head>
    <title>Questions</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{=URL('static', 'images/title.png')}}" />
</head>
<body>
    <div id="header">
        <img id="logo" src="{{=URL('static', 'images/wagMoreLogo.png')}}" width="200" height="152" alt="Woof!">
        <div id="title">
            <h1>Create your profile</h1>

        </div>
    </div>
    <center >
        <img style="margin-top: -67px" alt="Error" src="{{=URL('static', 'images/interests.png')}}", height="150px">
    </center>
    {{if(request.args(0)=="Remake"):}}
        <center >
            <h2 style="color:red;">Uops, apparently you forgot to fill this part of your profile</h2>
        </center>
    {{pass}}

<center><h2 style="margin:0px; text-decoration: underline">Questions 3/4 </h2></center>
            {{=form.custom.begin}}
        <div class="column">
           	<div class="question">    
            <b>A spontaneous road trip (with my pup!) sounds fun:</b> <div>{{=form.custom.widget.q11}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="question">

            <b>I am the life of the party:</b> <div>{{=form.custom.widget.q12}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
            <b>I am not shy meeting new people:</b> <div>{{=form.custom.widget.q13}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>    
        <div class="column">
            <div class="question">

            <b>I do not drink or do drugs: </b><div>{{=form.custom.widget.q14}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
            <b>I prefer to create a piece of art rather than to analyze a piece of art:</b> <div>{{=form.custom.widget.q15}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>  
		<input type="image" alt="Error" src="{{=URL('static','images/nextButton.png')}}", height="150px">
        {{=form.custom.end}}
</body>
</html>
